### Test SelectEmployer Endpoint
### ProviderId: 10005760

### Variables
@baseUrl = https://localhost:10234
@providerId = 10005760

### 1. Basic Request (No filters)
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json

### 2. With Search Term
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?searchTerm=Test%20Employer&useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json

### 3. With Search Term (Employer Name - Account Name format)
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?searchTerm=Employer%20Name%20-%20Account%20Name&useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json

### 4. With Sorting (by Employer Name, ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?sortField=EmployerAccountLegalEntityName&reverseSort=false&useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json

### 5. With Sorting (by Employer Name, descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?sortField=EmployerAccountLegalEntityName&reverseSort=true&useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json

### 6. With Sorting (by Account Name, ascending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?sortField=EmployerAccountName&reverseSort=false&useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json

### 7. With Sorting (by Account Name, descending)
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?sortField=EmployerAccountName&reverseSort=true&useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json

### 8. Combined Search and Sort
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?searchTerm=Test&sortField=EmployerAccountLegalEntityName&reverseSort=false&useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json

### 9. With UseLearnerData=true
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?useLearnerData=true
Accept: application/json

### 10. Empty search (should return all)
GET {{baseUrl}}/provider/{{providerId}}/unapproved/add/select-employer?searchTerm=&useLearnerData=false
Accept: application/json
